{"word":"ἄποπτος","slug":"ἄποπτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄποπτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀπόψομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ἀφοράω'><el>ἀφοράω</el></a>\n<p/><i>out of sight of, far away from</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>out of sight</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>ἐξ ἀπόπτου</el> from <i>a distance</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}